{
  "stem": "2830.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you put in one foot, you have to grab your other foot to take the other foot down.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then you put the other foot, you couldn't get this foot out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you got your shoes muddy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then you have to stand-- they give you a tin can or something for that water they give you?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a bowl.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you have a string.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You have to organize everything, a string to put around your waist to have that bowl hanging and that tin can to survive.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you don't have this, you don't survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because you don't have anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they give you-- finally, they gave you that supposed to be brown water and the ration of bread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you gobbled this up, and then you don't have anything left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they assign you to a block.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You come into those huts, and they assign you a place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they tend to out-- to our hut, to our-- one of those--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--wooden-- that you sleep on, with straw on it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There is three rows, one on-- some of them on the concrete, one on the middle, and one on top.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went up on the top.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we wind up with the ones we came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We try to, you know, keep together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were trying to keep together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I got up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The bed bugs, they were biting you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When they bite you, you know, it's like you-- you jump.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was just unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You have to scratch yourself all night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then you couldn't move, because we-- you're like herrings.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the morning, I saw one dead next to me, the one she came-- a sister of that Maria Brenner, her sister.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was already dead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She died right of, you know, typhus.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
